                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1658" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0266</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8786 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑州市三人行电子科技有限公司的微信营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">WeChat Marketing of Zhengzhou SanRenXing Electronic Technology Co.， Ltd.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王千，郭纨如等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑州大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑州市三人行电子科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三人行、微信营销、免费经济、顾客黏度、新媒体整合营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SanRenXing Electronic Technology Co.， Ltd.； WeChat Marketing； Free Economy； Customer Viscosity； New-media Integrated Marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑州三人行电子科技有限公司现有营销工具使用费用很高而且收效甚微。机缘巧合的是，一次停电的经历使得公司总经理王伟坚信：在当前的移动互联时代，微信营销必将成大器。于是他领导三人行积极开展微信营销活动。首先建立了三人行官方微网站，并运用微信公众账号的各种功能进行营销。2014年5月25日开始，三人行陆续推出了新的包括刮刮卡、优惠券、幸运大转盘、会员卡等微活动进行营销，使得顾客享受到很多数字化生存环境下免费经济的好处，顾客体验较好、顾客满意度提高、顾客黏度增加、口碑效应显现。但微信营销给三人行带来了精准营销的甜头的同时，也带来了很多困惑。王总的直观感受是要通过基于微信的新媒体整合营销传播来解决这些困惑，王总和他的三人行目前正在通向新媒体整合营销的路上……</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The cost of the existing marketing tools that SanRenXing Electronic Technology Co.， Ltd used now is relatively high， whereas these tools have little effect. An unexpectly power failure makes Wangwei， the CEO of SanRenXing believes that WeChat marketing is sure to succeed under the circumstance of mobile internet. So he leads the team to carry out the WeChat marketing activities. They firstly establish the company’s official website， then carry out marketing activities by using the pubic accounts of WeChat. At the beginning of May 25， 2014， the company launches new WeChat marketing activities， including scratching cards， coupons， Wheel of Fortune as well as the membership card. These micro activities make customers enjoy the free economy of the “being digital” environment. The effects of the WeChat are as follows： (1) initiating the customer’s engaging experience； (2) improving the customer’s satisfaction； (3) increasing the customer’s viscosity； (4) emerging the word of mouth effect. But “Each coins has two sides”. On the one hand， WeChat marketing enables the company to profit from precision marketing； on the other hand， it also causes a lot of confusions. In order to solve the present confusions of SanRenXing， Wangwei makes up his mind to launch a new-media integrated marketing based on WeChat. Now SanRenXing is on the way to integrate new-media marketing......</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销学》、《网络营销》、《新媒体整合营销传播》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新媒体整合营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
